{
  "name": "searchArtifacts",
  "description": "Returns a paginated list of all artifacts that match the provided search criteria.\n",
  "parameters": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "search": {
        "type": "string",
        "description": "The text to search."
      },
      "offset": {
        "default": 0,
        "type": "integer",
        "description": "The number of artifacts to skip before starting to collect the result set."
      },
      "limit": {
        "default": 20,
        "type": "integer",
        "description": "The number of artifacts to return."
      },
      "over": {
        "enum": [
          "everything",
          "name",
          "description",
          "labels"
        ],
        "type": "string",
        "description": "What fields to search."
      },
      "order": {
        "enum": [
          "asc",
          "desc"
        ],
        "type": "string",
        "description": "Sort order, ascending or descending."
      }
    },
    "required": [
      "offset",
      "limit"
    ]
  },
  "handler": "http",
  "request": {
    "method": "GET",
    "url": {
      "$uri": "http://apicurio.local/search/artifacts{?search,offset,limit,over,order}"
    }
  },
  "responses": {
    "200": {
      "$encode": "markdown",
      "$block": [
        {
          "$h1": "Object"
        },
        "Describes the response received when searching for artifacts.",
        "**Key properties:**",
        {
          "$ul": [
            "**artifacts**: The artifacts that matched the search criteria.",
            "**count**: The total number of artifacts that matched the search criteria."
          ]
        },
        {
          "$lang": "json",
          "$code": {
            "$encode": "json",
            "$indent": true,
            "$content": {
              "$": "$.body"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    "500": {
      "$encode": "markdown",
      "$block": [
        {
          "$h1": "Root Type for Error"
        },
        "All error responses, whether `4xx` or `5xx` will include one of these as the response\nbody.",
        "**Key properties:**",
        {
          "$ul": [
            "**detail**: Full details about the error.  This might contain a server stack trace, for example.",
            "**error_code**: The server-side error code.",
            "**message**: The short error message."
          ]
        },
        {
          "$lang": "json",
          "$code": {
            "$encode": "json",
            "$indent": true,
            "$content": {
              "$": "$.body"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
